Generated Narrative: ValueSet IMMZ.D1.DE103

  • Include these codes as defined in http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D1
    CodeDisplayDefinition
    DE104Primary seriesIndicates that the client received the primary vaccination series of a product/antigen. This is also applicable for antigens with one dose
    DE105Dose 0Indicates that the client received a dose of a product/ antigen that is not a part of the primary vaccination series and is administered before the primary vaccination series is provided
    DE106Supplementary doseIndicates that the client received a supplementary dose of a product/antigen
    DE107Booster doseIndicates that the client received booster dose of a product/antigen
